A new DemoCon schedule has been released!

We had to move some sessions, so if you were planning on seeing them, check their new dates or locations:

  • “Enhanced stable model” by Gregory Smith (Sept. 6, 2022, 9 a.m. → Sept. 24, 2022, 9 a.m.)
  • “Optional bifurcated attitude” by Martin Baker (Sept. 6, 2022, 9:30 a.m. → Sept. 6, 2022, 2:40 a.m.)
